	<h2>The Submission Process</h2>
	<h3>Submit Your Resume</h3> 
	<p>Once you are ready to submit your resume, you can follow the instructions on the homepage to choose your pricing option (see <a href="#pricing">pricing options</a>) and submit your resume (PDF or Word Document).</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Upon submission of your resume you will receive an email from us within 24 hours(Premium) or 72 hours(Free), depending on the package that you choose.</li>
		<li>The email will include an in-depth analysis of your resume along with suggested edits (see our <a href="#review_process">review process</a>).</li>
		<li>Once you make the revisions, you can resubmit your resume again for a second round review.</li> 
	</ul>
	
	<div id="pricing"><h3>Pricing Options</h3></div> 
	<p>There are two pricing options, Free and Premium. The free version is a trial review for you to sample our review process without having to make a financial commitment. The free review is very thorough and helpful, but with a lower level of detail than that of our Premium package. Our Premium package is the highest quality review that we currently offer and will absolutely solve all of your resume needs. </p>
